m inauthentic. This volume argues in favor of the authenticity of more than ten of these sermons, and for the first time, presents them in a critical edition. In addition, several sermons previously known to be authentic are presented for the first time in a complete version.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Latin.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aSermons, LatinvEarly works to 1800. 0aSermons, LatinxHistory and criticism. 4aAugustinus von Hippo. 4aPredigten. 4aSpätantike. 4akritische Edition. 7aRELIGION / Sermons / Christian.2bisacsh  aAugustine.  acritical edition.  alate antiquity.  asermons.1 aPartoens, Gert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWeidmann, Clemens, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWeidmann, Clemens, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1z978311076251808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET PHILOSOPHIE DES MITTELALTERS ONLINEz9783110514827oZDB-23-PHM08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theology, Relig. Studies, Jewish Studies 2015z9783110438727oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978311033399240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311033664140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110336641423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110336641/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-076251-8  DG Plus DeG Package 2015 Part 1b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA1